epd-dither
==========

This crate ships one third-party asset, licensed independently of the
crate source code. Per-asset licence text lives under `LICENSES/`,
mirroring the asset's path within the source tree.


assets/HDR_L_0.png
------------------
A 256×256 16-bit grayscale blue-noise tile from Christoph Peters'
"Free blue noise textures" distribution
(http://momentsingraphics.de/BlueNoise.html), generated using the
void-and-cluster method [Ulichney 1993].
Released into the public domain via Creative Commons CC0 1.0.
